<div class="title">Never Ever Want To Do That Much Again</div>
<div class="substance">Methamphetamine & Amphetamines (Dexedrine)</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Green+Ninja&Exact=1">Green Ninja</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Green Ninja. "Never Ever Want To Do That Much Again: An Experience with Methamphetamine & Amphetamines (Dexedrine) (exp43031)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Sep 1, 2007. erowid.org/exp/43031</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
<tr><td></td><td width="15">&nbsp;</td></tr>
